  {
    "hotel_id": "1636324",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/papo-a-hotel/hotel/kaohsiung-tw.html",
    "name": "PAPO'A HOTEL",
    "detail": "Hotel is very new, clean and modern. Loved the hotel decor! Located within 2 mins walk to the rear exit of Kaohsiung Main Station (train not MRT). MRT entrance is located at the front entrance of the train station which is a easy 5-7mins by taking a short cut via the train station. Super convenient yet away from the noisy street traffic. Hotel room is more spacious than expected. Well designed to truly maximise space- Clothes rack rather wardrobe. The quad room has 2 queen beds which were very comfy. Breakfast comes in a set- a local dish with fruits platter and soya milk. The hotel is very thoughtful to make sure guests get different breakfast everyday. Those who prefers western breakfast, can book a room without breakfast as Macdonalds is located at the front entrance of the train station which is 5-7 mins walk away. Overall, I'm a very satisfied guest and highly recommended if you are in Kaohsiung! ",
